WE as poets, Artists and performers MUST uphold our responsibility (without stripping ourselves of creativity) uphold how we plant seed. it must be to direct, corall, and guide in GOODNESS. AGAIN...My Love for ALL walks of life and my consistent conversing and Love of Christ and his own Love for ALL walks of life must be advocates of purity and Unity as family! GOD BLESS ALL!***
